## 2. Tech stack

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|-------|-----------|-----------|
| Frontend | React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS | Single codebase for 3 apps. Type safety. Utility-first styling. |
| Build tool | Vite | Fast HMR, native ESM, optimized production builds. TypeScript/React support out of the box. |
| UI components | shadcn/ui | Accessible components built on Radix UI. Copy-paste into codebase for full ownership and customization. |
| Backend | Deno TypeScript (Supabase Edge Functions) | Built-in auth, RLS for RBAC, Edge Functions for token logic, Realtime for kiosk. Type-safe backend. Eliminates custom API for solo dev. |
| Database | Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Realtime) | Managed Postgres with built-in auth and RLS. Realtime subscriptions for kiosk. |
| QR generation | qrcode.react | Client-side QR rendering. No server-side image generation needed. |
| State management | TanStack Query (react-query) | Server state caching, background refetch, optimistic updates for dashboard. |
| Validation | Zod | Runtime type validation for all API responses. |
| Deployment | Vercel (frontend) + Supabase (backend) | Zero-config deploys. Supabase handles DB + auth + functions. |

**Monorepo structure**: 3 apps (`customer-form`, `kiosk`, `admin-dashboard`) + 1 shared package (`shared` for types, constants, Supabase client).

