## 3. User roles and permissions

### 3.1 Customer (anonymous)
- **Who**: End user in-store (purchased or browsing)
- **Auth**: None. Anonymous access via QR scan.
- **Can do**: Submit feedback via QR scan. One submission per token.
- **Cannot do**: View dashboard, configure anything, access admin features.

### 3.2 Kiosk Service Accounts
- **Who**: Dedicated Supabase Auth users, one per physical tablet. MVP: 2 accounts — one for browse zone, one for billing zone.
- **Auth**: Email + password, **no 2FA**. Machine identity, not a human login.
- **Session**: Persistent refresh token stored on device. Survives reboots. Never expires unless revoked.
- **Role**: `kiosk` (stored in `app_metadata`). Enforced via RLS.
- **Can do**: Call `mint-token` Edge Function only. No other DB access.
- **Cannot do**: Access admin dashboard, read feedback data, revoke tokens, change zone config.
- **Independence**: Each kiosk session is fully independent. Admin logging off has zero effect on any kiosk.
- **Provisioning**: Admin creates kiosk from the admin dashboard (name + branch + zone + section) → system creates Supabase Auth user → admin sees credentials once → IT stores credentials in tablet `.env` → done permanently.

**MVP kiosk accounts:**

| Account | Zone | Section config | Tablet |
|---------|------|---------------|--------|
| `kiosk-browse@chennaisilks.local` | Browse | Set in admin panel (e.g. Sarees, Shirts, Trousers) | Tablet 1 |
| `kiosk-billing@chennaisilks.local` | Billing | Set in admin panel. MVP: admin-generated QR. Post-MVP: auto from POS via SKU. | Tablet 2 / counter |

### 3.3 Store Admin
- **Who**: Store manager or operations staff
- **Auth**: Email + password + TOTP 2FA via Supabase Auth. Human login, session-based.
- **Session**: Short-lived JWT. Expires. Must re-login. Cannot access kiosk app.
- **Can do**: Configure zones, manage kiosks, view zone-specific dashboard, export CSV, revoke tokens, manage product sections.
- **Cannot do**: Access MD cross-zone comparison views (role-separated via RLS). Cannot mint tokens directly.

### 3.4 MD / Owner
- **Who**: Managing Director or business owner
- **Auth**: Email + password + TOTP 2FA via Supabase Auth. Human login, session-based.
- **Session**: Short-lived JWT. Expires. Must re-login. Cannot access kiosk app.
- **Can do**: View all zone dashboards, cross-zone comparison, section heatmap, trend analysis, export CSV.
- **Cannot do**: Configure zones, manage kiosks, revoke tokens. Strictly read-only. Cannot mint tokens directly.

