### 6.6 audit_logs

Immutable log of all admin-initiated state changes. INSERT-only (no UPDATE, no DELETE ever).

| Field | Type | Constraints | Notes |
|-------|------|------------|-------|
| log_id | UUID | PK, auto-generated | |
| user_id | UUID | FK → auth.users, NOT NULL | Admin or MD who performed the action |
| action | TEXT | NOT NULL | e.g. 'revoke_token', 'create_zone', 'provision_kiosk', 'export_csv' |
| resource_type | TEXT | nullable | e.g. 'token', 'zone', 'kiosk', 'export' |
| resource_id | UUID | nullable | ID of the affected resource |
| context | JSONB | nullable | Structured data: old/new values, reason, row counts |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | NOT NULL, DEFAULT now() | |

**When to log:**
- Token revocation (`action='revoke_token'`, `resource_id=token_id`)
- Zone creation/update (`action='create_zone'` / `'update_zone'`, `resource_id=zone_id`)
- Kiosk provisioning (`action='provision_kiosk'`, `resource_id=kiosk_id`)
- CSV exports (`action='export_csv'`, `context={date_range, zone_filter, row_count}`)

**Never log:** Customer feedback submissions, token minting (high volume), token validation checks.

**RLS**: Admin and MD can SELECT. No INSERT policy for users — only Edge Functions via service role. No UPDATE or DELETE policies.

