## 12. Non-functional requirements

| Category | Requirement |
|----------|------------|
| Performance | API latency < 200ms. Token minting < 500ms. QR generation < 1s on kiosk. Customer form loads < 2s on 3G. |
| Availability | 99.9% uptime for feedback API. Kiosk works offline for idle state (reconnects for minting). |
| Security | 2FA for admin/MD. RBAC via Supabase RLS. TLS 1.3 in transit. Encryption at rest (Supabase default). Audit logs for all admin actions (immutable). |
| Privacy | No PII stored. No IP addresses. No device fingerprints. Data minimization. Retention policy enforced. |
| Accessibility | WCAG 2.1 AA. All tap targets ≥ 48dp. Keyboard navigable admin. Screen-reader friendly labels. |
| Observability | Structured logs for token mint/validate/consume. Metrics for submission rates and error rates. Alerting on sustained errors. |
| Internationalisation | English only MVP. Locale-ready: all 30 UI strings in `en.json`. Adding `ta.json` is a config change, not a code change. |

