## 13. Removed from original spec (with rationale)

| Item | Rationale |
|------|-----------|
| Auto-rotate QR per zone | Per-transaction tokens eliminate rotation. Each QR is single-use. |
| Manual rotation | Simplified to revocation only. No rotation concept exists. |
| Geofence radius | Poor indoor GPS accuracy in retail. Single-use tokens provide anti-spam. |
| rotation_interval_min | Replaced by token_ttl_min. Tokens minted on-demand. |
| Anomaly detection (MVP) | Moved to Could Have. Needs real data. Manual revocation covers edge cases. |
| device_token / fingerprinting | Replaced by single-use tokens. No need for device tracking when each QR is one-time-use. |

